<hw>6</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>one more than five; denoting
a quantity consisting of six items or units; -- representing the number
six as an Arabic numeral</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> six, vi, half dozen, half a dozen</syn>⟦br⟧
